00:35:11.100 --> 00:35:14.480
For example, here
are three managers.

00:35:14.480 --> 00:35:18.900
All three of these managers have
a 15% expected rate of return.

00:35:22.020 --> 00:35:25.130
But they have different betas.

00:35:25.130 --> 00:35:26.900
And so the question
